text: New Start (Hungarian: Új Kezdet, ÚK or UK) was a conservative centrist party in Hungary. == History == The party was founded in 2016 in Gödöllő. In 2018, it ran in the elections alongside the LMP but did not win any seats. It also participated in the 2024 local elections but failed to gain any seats. On February 24, 2025, the party dissolved itself without a legal successor. == References == Category:Defunct political parties in Hungary Category:Centrist parties Category:Conservative parties Category:2016 establishments in Europe Category:21st-century establishments in Hungary Category:2020s disestablishments in Europe
